[CENTER][SIZE=5][COLOR=#5e4fa2][B]━━━━━━━━━━ Overview ━━━━━━━━━━[/B][/COLOR][/SIZE][/CENTER]

[B]xInventories[/B] is a powerful and modern per-world inventory management plugin built specifically for Paper 1.20.5+ servers. Keep player inventories, experience, health, hunger, potion effects, and ender chests completely separate across different worlds or world groups.

Whether you're running a survival server with a creative world, a minigame network, or a skyblock server with multiple islands, xInventories gives you complete control over how player data is managed across your worlds.

[CENTER][SIZE=5][COLOR=#5e4fa2][B]━━━━━━━━━━ Features ━━━━━━━━━━[/B][/COLOR][/SIZE][/CENTER]

[B][SIZE=4]Core Features[/SIZE][/B]
[LIST]
[*][B]Per-World Inventories[/B] - Separate inventories for different worlds or world groups
[*][B]Per-GameMode Inventories[/B] - Optionally separate inventories by gamemode
[*][B]Flexible World Groups[/B] - Group multiple worlds together to share inventories
[*][B]Regex Pattern Matching[/B] - Automatically assign worlds using patterns (e.g., skyblock_.*)
[*][B]Multiple Storage Backends[/B] - Choose from YAML, SQLite, or MySQL
[*][B]High-Performance Caching[/B] - Caffeine-powered write-behind caching
[*][B]Admin GUI[/B] - Visual interface for managing groups, worlds, and player inventories
[*][B]Backup & Restore[/B] - Create and restore backups of all player data
[*][B]Data Migration[/B] - Seamlessly migrate between storage backends
[*][B]Full Developer API[/B] - Comprehensive API with events and subscriptions
[*][B]PlaceholderAPI Support[/B] - Built-in placeholders for scoreboards and more
[/LIST]

[B][SIZE=4]v1.1.0 Features[/SIZE][/B]
[LIST]
[*][B]Inventory Versioning[/B] - Automatic version history with rollback capability
[*][B]Death Recovery[/B] - Recover inventories lost on death
[*][B]Player State Separation[/B] - Per-group statistics, advancements, and recipes
[*][B]Templates[/B] - Pre-defined inventory templates for starter kits and loadouts
[*][B]Item Restrictions[/B] - Whitelist/blacklist items per group
[*][B]NBT Filters[/B] - Advanced filtering by enchantments, custom model data, name/lore patterns
[*][B]Shared Slots[/B] - Share specific slots across all groups
[*][B]Conditional Groups[/B] - Dynamic groups based on permissions, time, or PlaceholderAPI
[*][B]World Group Inheritance[/B] - Groups inherit settings from parent groups
[*][B]Temporary Groups[/B] - Time-limited group assignments for events/minigames
[*][B]Inventory Locking[/B] - Temporarily lock inventories with bypass permissions
[*][B]Audit Logging[/B] - Track all inventory modifications with full history
[*][B]Bulk Operations[/B] - Apply actions to all players in a group
[*][B]Anti-Dupe Detection[/B] - Detect potential item duplication exploits
[*][B]Inventory Search[/B] - Search across all player inventories
[*][B]Statistics Dashboard[/B] - Plugin performance metrics
[*][B]Vault Economy[/B] - Per-group economy balances
[*][B]LuckPerms Contexts[/B] - Current group as LuckPerms context
[*][B]Folia Support[/B] - Multi-threaded server compatibility
[*][B]Plugin Import[/B] - Import from PerWorldInventory, MultiVerse-Inventories, MyWorlds
[*][B]Cross-Server Sync[/B] - Redis-based sync for BungeeCord/Velocity networks
[*][B]Inventory Merge[/B] - Merge two groups' inventories with conflict resolution
[*][B]Export/Import JSON[/B] - Export inventories for external tools or backup
[*][B]20+ GUI Screens[/B] - Comprehensive admin interface for all features
[/LIST]

