[CENTER][SIZE=5][COLOR=#5e4fa2][B]━━━━━━━━━━ Installation ━━━━━━━━━━[/B][/COLOR][/SIZE][/CENTER]

[LIST=1]
[*]Download the jar file (lightweight ~1.7MB)
[*]Place it in your server's [FONT=Courier New]plugins/[/FONT] folder
[*]Restart your server (Paper will automatically download required libraries)
[*]Configure [FONT=Courier New]plugins/xInventories/config.yml[/FONT]
[*]Set up world groups in [FONT=Courier New]plugins/xInventories/groups.yml[/FONT]
[/LIST]

[B]Note:[/B] xInventories uses Paper's library loader to automatically download dependencies at startup. This keeps the jar small and ensures compatible library versions.

